title: Version 1.0.1
message:
Version 1.0.1

Updated to the new official Vertcoin icon

title: Getting source back up to date.
message: Getting source back up to date.

title: Added support for multiple providers, and added Coinbase.
message: Added support for multiple providers, and added Coinbase.

title: Changes based on pull request by staticfish.
message:
Changes based on pull request by staticfish.

Updated layout to use dp for text so it won't be affected by user's system font settings.

title: Support minutes, hours, or days selections for poll settings.
message: Support minutes, hours, or days selections for poll settings.

title: Fixed Australian and Canadian dollar displays.
message:
Fixed Australian and Canadian dollar displays.

Adjusted text size to account for $100 threshold.
